            "texttype":"Online",
            "textpurpose":"Provenance",
            "textentryhtml":"<p>\n\tBy September 1976, Gillett G. Griffin (1928-2016), Princeton, NJ [1]; promised bequest Gillett G. Griffin to the Princeton University Art Museum.\n</p>\n<p>\n\tNotes:\n\t<br />\n\t[1] According to dated slides (GG9000714-5) in the Griffin archive.\n</p>",
            "remarks":null
